# Mask Configuration
# Define all masks, their textures, abilities, and level scaling

# Ability Types:
#   PASSIVE - Always active when worn
#   ON_HIT - Triggers when hitting an enemy
#   ON_DAMAGED - Triggers when taking damage
#   ON_KILL - Triggers when killing an entity
#   ON_MINE - Triggers when breaking blocks
#   ON_FISH - Triggers when fishing

# Effect Types:
#   POTION - Apply potion effect (uses potion-type, duration, amplifier)
#   DAMAGE_MULTIPLIER - Multiply damage dealt
#   DAMAGE_REDUCTION - Reduce damage taken
#   HEALTH_BOOST - Add extra hearts
#   SPAWN_MINIONS - Spawn mobs to fight for you
#   BONUS_DROPS - Increase mob drops
#   BONUS_XP - Increase XP gained
#   SPECIAL - Custom coded effect (uses special-id)

